Mo thi TOEIC Part 5: Loi cu hi v t
vng
Chn p n n thun bng cch da vo ng ngha
Thng thng, cc cu hi t vng TOEIC Part 5 l nhng cu c cc p n ABCD l
nhng t hon ton khc nhau, khng thuc cng mt h t (family words) v khng th
loi suy lun bng ng php.
V d: Poor visibility has forced the airline to _____ the flight's departure time from 6
o'clock to 8 o'clock. (Tm nhn km buc hng hng khng phi _____ thi gian khi
hnh ca chuyn bay t 6 gi sang 8 gi.)
A. depend (ph thuc).
B. distort (lm mo m).
C. demand (yu cu).
D. delay (tr hon).
Vi cc dng cu hi nh trn th phng php duy nht chn c cu ng chnh l
da vo ngha ca ton cu. V da vo phn dch i km ta c th thy p n D l
p n ph hp cho cu trn.
Vic bit c cng nhiu t vng TOEIC s gip chng ta vt qua nhng cu ny d
dng hn. Tuy nhin nu trong trng hp cu trn m bn ch bit c ngha ca 3 t
depend, distort v demand thi th cng d dng suy on c p n ph hp l
delay ng khng no?!
Chn p n bng cch suy lun da vo nhng t i chung vi nhau (collocations)
Collocation hiu nm na chnh l nhng t c kt hp vi nhau to thnh mt
cm t c ngha v thng c dng trong cuc sng hng ngy. V d cng ch mang
ngha l mu en nhng ngi Vit ta c nhng cm t khc nhau dng ch mu
en nh ch mc hay mo mun vy .
Tng t trong ting Anh s c mt s cm t i chung vi nhau, v d nh:
Make the bed dn dp ging.
Do the homework lm bi tp.
Take a risk lm liu, mo him.
Give someone advice cho ai li khuyn.
Mt s dng collocation thng thy trong thi TOEIC:
Trng t + tnh t: completely satisfied = hon ton tha mn (ch khng ni
downright satisfied).
Tnh t + danh t: heavy rain = ma ln (ch khng ni big rain).
Danh t + danh t: a surge of anger = cn thnh n (ch khng ni a rush of anger).
Danh t + ng t: lions roar = s t gm (ch khng ni lions shout).
ng t + danh t: commit suicide = t st (ch khng ni undertake suicide).
ng t + mt cm gii t: burst into tears = a khc (ch khng ni blow up in
tears).
ng t + trng t: wave frantically = vy tay lin tc (ch khng ni wave
feverishly).
Lu cc t c cch vit gn ging nhau d gy nhm ln
Trong ting Anh c mt s cp t d gy nhm ln m nu chng ta khng k th s
rt d ri vo by ca thi TOEIC Part 5.
Mt s cp t tiu biu c th k ra l:
Accept (chp nhn) v Except (ngoi tr).
Adverse (bt li) v Averse (chng li).
Advice (li khuyn) v Advise (khuyn rn).
Affect (gy nh hng) v Effect (s nh hng).
Assent (s ng ) v Ascent (s i ln).
Brake (thng, phanh xe) v Break (s v).
Complement (b sung) v Compliment (khen ngi).
Council (hi ng) v Counsel (khuyn).
Desert (sa mc) v Dessert (mn trng ming).
Discrete (ring bit) v Discreet (thn trng).
Ensure (bo m) v Insure (bo him).
Everyday (mi ngy tnh t) v Every day (mi ngy trng t).
Hard (kh, chm ch) v Hardly (hu nh khng).
Historic (kinh in) v Historical (thuc v lch s).
Lose (nh mt) v Loose (rng, lng lo).
Principal (hiu trng) v Principle (chnh).
Site (v tr) v sight (tm nhn, th lc).
Stationary (ng yn) v Stationery (dng c vn phng).
Story (cu chuyn) v Storey (tng).
